This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for personality classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with the intersection of computer science and linguistics. The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely category. The paper also involves the use of semantic resources, which makes cs.LG (Learning) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) likely categories. Finally, the paper involves the use of high-level concepts and emotions, which makes cs.SD (Sound) a possible category as well.
